，並將照片上載到個人Facebook、微信朋友圈、IG等，並在帖內輸入Hashtag：  #全民撐警    #守護香港 <br />\n<br />\n2.見到警察時，比個微笑😁，打聲招呼，講聲「辛苦曬，多謝你！」<br />\n<br />\n3.到警方Facebook 留言點讚👍🏼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2F&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=6055fb1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/</a><br />\n<br />\n4.在網上填寫嘉許表格，對警員進行讚賞🥇<a href=\"https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLT_TO_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FEGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI%2Fereport_details%3Freport%3DCMPLT_TO_POLICE_OFCR%26fontSize%3D100&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=1517ba71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLT_TO_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5.按以下連結查詢附近警署🏢地址，以方便大家前往慰問🍵<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GPMs6x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GPMs6x&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=12bd9d31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GPMs6x</a></span></span>"}]}